snippet.title: Secret Tea Garden  - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Available here: https://angusbeer.itch.io/secret-tea-garden

Note: I've reuploaded the trailer as YouTube recognised the original as a "YouTube Short", which it isn't. 

Secret Tea Garden is a game where you brew and deliver tea for an endless crowd of uniquely generated characters! 

This was my entry for 2020's Low Rez jam, a challenge to make a game in 64x64 pixels!

Secret Tea Garden (c) Angus Beer 2020
Music (c) William Burroughs 2020
